                                        </div>
                                        <div class="md:col-span-3 col-span-5 col-start-2 content-center">
                                            <p class="text-neutral-950 font-bold">Guldberg Kiosk</p>
                                            <p class="text-neutral-950">Guldbergsgade 24,</p>
                                            <p class="text-neutral-950">2200 København n</p>
